      "data": "<div id=\"article_content\" class=\"article_content\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><p style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">通过VMWare共享windows上的文件夹，通过终端进行 &nbsp;rpm &nbsp;安装软件包时，提示can't create transaction lock on /var/lib/rpm/.rpm.lock错误。</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">错误原因：权限问题<br>解决方法：<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 26px;\">在终端输入“su”和密码，登录<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">root</span>，以root身份登录就不会有提示</span></p><div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 26px;\"><br></span></div></div>"
